* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|Why can't you sleep, what's wrong?}}
** '''Player:''' Why can't you sleep, what's wrong?
** '''Brother Omad:''' It's brother Androe's son! With his constant: Waaaaaah! Waaaaaaaaah! Androe said it's natural, but it's so annoying!
** '''Player:''' I suppose that's what kids do.
** '''Brother Omad:''' He was fine, up until last week! Thieves broke in! They stole his favourite sleeping blanket!
** '''Brother Omad:''' Now he won't rest until it's returned... ...and that means neither can I!
** {{tselect|Start the Monk's Friend quest?}}
** {{topt|Yes.}}
*** '''Player:''' Can I help at all?
*** '''Brother Omad:''' Please do. We won't be able to help you as we are peaceful men but we would be grateful for your help!
*** '''Player:''' Where are they?
*** '''Brother Omad:''' They hide in a secret cave in the forest. It's hidden under a ring of stones. Please, bring back the blanket!
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|No.}}
*** '''Player:''' I'm sorry to hear that! I hope you find his blanket.
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|Sorry! I'm too busy to hear your problems!}}
** '''Player:''' Sorry! I'm too busy to hear your problems!
** {{tact|end}}

===Talking to brother Omad before retrieving the blanket===
* '''Player:''' Hello.
* '''Brother Omad:''' *yawn*...oh, hello again...*yawn*
* '''Brother Omad:''' Please tell me you have the blanket.
* '''Player:''' I'm afraid not.
* '''Brother Omad:''' I need some sleep!
* {{tact|end}}

===Monk overhead===
* '''Monk:''' {{overhead|*yawn*}}
* {{tact|end}}

==Child's blanket==
===Entering the stone circle===
* {{mes|A ladder mysteriously appears.}}

===Talking to Brother Omad after retrieving the blanket===
* '''Player:''' Hello.
* '''Brother Omad:''' *yawn*...oh, hello again...*yawn*
* '''Brother Omad:''' Please tell me you have the blanket.
* '''Player:''' Yes! I've recovered it from the clutches of the evil thieves!
* {{tbox|pic=Child's blanket detail.png|You hand the monk the childs blanket.}}
* '''Brother Omad:''' Really, that's excellent, well done! Maybe now I will be able to get some rest.
* '''Brother Omad:''' *yawn*..I'm off to bed! Farewell brave traveller! {{^|Here is where he actually takes the blanket.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to a Monk after retrieving the blanket===
* '''Monk:''' Can't wait for the party!
* {{tact|end}}

==Brother Cedric==
===Talking to Brother Cedric before agreeing to find him===
* '''Player:''' Hello.
* '''Brother Cedric:''' Honey, money, woman and wine!
* '''Player:''' Are you ok?
* '''Brother Cedric:''' Yesshh...hic up...beautiful!
* '''Player:''' Take care old monk.
* '''Brother Cedric:''' La..di..da..hic..up!
* {{mes|The old monk has had too much to drink.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Brother Omad again===
* '''Player:''' Hello, how are you?
* '''Brother Omad:''' Much better now I'm sleeping well! Now I can organise the party.
* '''Player:''' Ooh! What party?
* '''Brother Omad:''' The son of Brother Androe's birthday party. He's going to be one year old!
* '''Player:''' That's sweet!
* '''Brother Omad:''' It's also a great excuse for a drink!
* '''Brother Omad:''' We just need Brother Cedric to return with the wine.
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|Who's Brother Cedric?}}
** '''Player:''' Who's Brother Cedric?
** '''Brother Omad:''' Cedric is a member of the order too. We sent him out three days ago to collect wine. But he didn't return!
** '''Brother Omad:''' He most probably got drunk and lost in the forest!
** '''Brother Omad:''' I don't suppose you could look for him?
** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
** {{topt|I've no time for that, sorry.}}
*** '''Player:''' I've no time for that, sorry.
*** '''Brother Omad:''' Okay traveller, take care.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|Where should I look?}}
*** '''Player:''' Where should I look?
*** '''Brother Omad:''' Oh, he won't be far. Probably out in the forest.
*** '''Player:''' Ok, I'll go and find him.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|Can I come to the party?}}
*** '''Player:''' Can I come to the party?
*** '''Brother Omad:''' Of course, but we need the wine first.
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|Enjoy it! I'll see you soon!}}
** '''Player:''' Enjoy it! I'll see you soon!
** '''Brother Omad:''' Take care traveller.
** {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Brother Omad before finding Brother Cedric===
* '''Player:''' Hello brother Omad.
* '''Brother Omad:''' Hello adventurer, have you found Brother Cedric?
* '''Player:''' Not yet.
* '''Brother Omad:''' Well, keep looking, we need that wine!
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Brother Cedric===
* '''Player:''' Brother Cedric are you okay?
* '''Brother Cedric:''' Yeesshhh, I'm very, very drunk..hic..up..
* '''Player:''' Brother Omad needs the wine for the party.
* '''Brother Cedric:''' Oh dear, oh dear, I knew I had to do something!
* '''Brother Cedric:''' Pleashhh, find me a jug of water. Once I'm sober I'll 'elp you take the wine back.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Brother Cedric before getting water===
* '''Player:''' Are you okay?
* '''Brother Cedric:''' Hic up! Oh my head! I need a jug of water.
* '''Player:''' I'll see if I can get some.
* '''Brother Cedric:''' Thanks! *hic*
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Brother Omad after finding Brother Cedric===
* '''Brother Omad:''' Hello adventurer, have you found Brother Cedric?
* '''Player:''' Yes I've seen him, he's a bit drunk!
* '''Brother Omad:''' Well, try your best to get him back here!
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Brother Cedric with water===
* '''Player:''' Are you okay?
* '''Brother Cedric:''' Hic up! Oh my head! I need a jug of water.
* '''Player:''' Cedric! Here, drink! I have some water.
* '''Brother Cedric:''' Good stuff, my head's spinning!
* {{tbox|pic=Jug of water detail.png|You hand the monk a jug of water.}}
* '''Brother Cedric:''' {{overhead|Gulp... gulp!}}
* '''Brother Cedric:''' Aah! That's better!
* '''Brother Cedric:''' Now I just need to fix this cart and we can go party.
* '''Brother Cedric:''' Could you help?
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|No, I've helped enough monks today!}}
** '''Player:''' No, I've helped enough monks today!
** '''Brother Cedric:''' In that case I'd better drink more wine! It helps me think.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|Yes, I'd be happy to!}}
** '''Player:''' Yes, I'd be happy to!
** '''Brother Cedric:''' Excellent, I just need some wood. Some plain logs, or maybe a basic plank.
** '''Player:''' OK, I'll see what I can find.
** {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Brother Cedric after giving him water before accepting to help with the cart===
* '''Brother Cedric:''' Now I just need to fix this cart and we can go party.
* '''Brother Cedric:''' Could you help?
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|No, I've helped enough monks today!}}
** {{tact|above}}
* {{topt|Yes, I'd be happy to!}}
** {{tact|above}}

===Talking to Brother Omad after giving Brother Cedric water===
* '''Player:''' Hello again brother Omad.
* '''Brother Omad:''' Hello adventurer, where's Brother Cedric?
* '''Player:''' He's having a bit of trouble with his cart.
* '''Brother Omad:''' Hmmm! Maybe you could help?
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Brother Cedric before getting some wood===
* '''Brother Cedric:''' Did you manage to get some wood?
* '''Player:''' Not yet, I'm afraid.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Brother Cedric while holding some wood===
* '''Brother Cedric:''' Did you manage to get some wood?
* {{tcond|If the player has logs:}}
** {{tbox|pic=Logs detail.png|You show Cedric some logs.}}
* {{tcond|If the player has a plank:}}
** {{tbox|pic=Plank detail.png|You show Cedric a wooden plank.}}
* '''Player:''' Here you go!
* '''Brother Cedric:''' Well done! Now I'll fix this cart. You head back to Brother Omad and tell him I'll be there soon.
* '''Player:''' Ok! I'll see you later!
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Brother Cedric again before returning===
* '''Player:''' Hello Cedric.
* '''Brother Cedric:''' Hi, I'm almost done here. Could you tell Omad that I'll be back soon?
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Brother Omad after finding and helping Brother Cedric===
* '''Player:''' Hi Omad, Brother Cedric is on his way!
* '''Brother Omad:''' Good! Good! Now we can party!
* '''Brother Omad:''' I have little to repay you with but please, take these runes.
* {{tbox|pic=Law rune detail.png|Brother Omad gives you 8 Law Runes.}}{{^|If inventory is full, runes appear on the floor after you finish dancing.}}
* '''Player:''' Thanks Brother Omad!
* '''Brother Omad:''' OK, let's party!
* {{tact|Dancing cutscene begins}}

